{"id": "1255087270348722228", "channel_id": "1255087270348722228", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "摸完325就开始摸350，除了3-3（希洛真不如凯刻斯轮椅吧）重开多次，其他都是一次通关，达成壮举！所以说不要说没限定玩不了玩不了，没限定还能融灾350呢！（限时命轮只带了个莉莉活动的SR，一个限定SSR角色和命轮都没有）录屏得晚点发B站，因为3-3没录上，晚点有空重打", "timestamp": "2024-06-25T09:08:43.645000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255087271087181875", "filename": "Screenshot_20240625_164526_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 215038, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255087270348722228/1255087271087181875/Screenshot_20240625_164526_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cb8f1b&is=69ca3d9b&hm=30b7234060350ad0ec510562dd523dc3cdfd731ff153e80c7d01431712f6d29c&"}, {"id": "1255087271452082368", "filename": "Screenshot_20240625_164530_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 215704, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255087270348722228/1255087271452082368/Screenshot_20240625_164530_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cb8f1b&is=69ca3d9b&hm=b29533a04b3dc00a554a711e7882a53e8e8a5edd9fc77a6d7266393203b9c41a&"}, {"id": "1255087271833505853", "filename": "Screenshot_20240625_164533_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 215748, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255087270348722228/1255087271833505853/Screenshot_20240625_164533_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cb8f1b&is=69ca3d9b&hm=4555bef215a0ab35592d12bcbecea62d77ad9ba5560dae5ac66d986950a024e9&"}, {"id": "1255087272211120180", "filename": "Screenshot_20240625_164539_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 210527, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255087270348722228/1255087272211120180/Screenshot_20240625_164539_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cb8f1c&is=69ca3d9c&hm=e24e4eab638014547ac12d96816d18ef0d98feb887558cfca41ec6e84193a1cc&"}, {"id": "1255087272588738580", "filename": "Screenshot_20240625_164550_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 208749, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255087270348722228/1255087272588738580/Screenshot_20240625_164550_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cb8f1c&is=69ca3d9c&hm=1bde21c97a2b82002a0db05fcc931c5d55f3ca65803d8a46bb3bb7e05cef8100&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255087270348722228", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全常驻本期融灾禁区350分", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1255089330473533502", "channel_id": "1255087270348722228", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "造物榜上可查，5-3这队精英就掉了一次死抗，不然没法吃下，造物回转还行，主要是七鳃鳗和水手哨回血，后期血量压低了雷亚几乎没用，全是菲和七鳃鳗在顶血压，观众选艾继丝，只在5连击出牌都可以（因为大变活人我就没打死过），4-3全程静海，盾击，偷力量，打得很随意，死抗都不带掉的，3-3借来的凯刻斯带队，真轮椅，静海吊打精英孕妇，2-3我自身凯刻斯启灵练度不高，打得有点勉强，造物也没买到，还多吃了180地板伤害，其实不用五次死抗那么极限的，1-3叠盾就完了，莉兹毒跟蜘蛛钥令差不多，（加强莉兹！）", "timestamp": "2024-06-25T09:16:54.817000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255087270348722228", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "全常驻本期融灾禁区350分", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1243105047332524043"]}
