{"id": "1255166767169540207", "channel_id": "1255166767169540207", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "只要给队伍里配一个子宫命伦，前提是2叠以上，可以无视全对掉狂气开不出大招的麻烦，这2算力加2抽牌，直接无敌了!这可是日月轮盘+才有的效果啊!", "timestamp": "2024-06-25T14:24:37.164000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255166767534178475", "filename": "Record_2024-06-25-22-06-00.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2320139, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255166767169540207/1255166767534178475/Record_2024-06-25-22-06-00.mp4?ex=69cbd925&is=69ca87a5&hm=3206c7a3802dc7b0df8bdda812aaef0452cf276c0dbef406c3c0a24ea691dfa7&"}, {"id": "1255166768041820231", "filename": "Record_2024-06-25-22-15-19.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2806750, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255166767169540207/1255166768041820231/Record_2024-06-25-22-15-19.mp4?ex=69cbd925&is=69ca87a5&hm=755f89df3b730bd8b0fc36df5dce0c437396ac72121cf7edbde5580604426153&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255166767169540207", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "给大家推荐一个攻略啊，这个技巧太猛了。", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179734373019748", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1255167126545760286", "channel_id": "1255166767169540207", "type": 0, "author_id": "1045141709580927067", "author_name": "luoqixikiss", "author_bot": false, "content": "这个就是米粒银匙配上子宫命伦，这就是最强搭配吧🤣", "timestamp": "2024-06-25T14:26:02.846000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255166767169540207", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "给大家推荐一个攻略啊，这个技巧太猛了。", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179734373019748", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
